Add macOS Mojave and Catalina

These were not yet explicitly recognized.

Rename OS X to macOS

Since 2016, Apple rebranded 'OS X' to 'macOS'.
This commit changes the UI to make sure this is reflected in
django-user-sessions as well.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MacOS#macOS
